results.deck: Founded on April 2, 1999, Cing was created as a means of providing gamers with new and unique video game experiences. They work mainly on adventure games, and all their games but one have been published exclusively on Nintendo systems.
results.description: On March 1, 2010, Cing filed for bankruptcy. The company has not confirmed whether it will go out of business entirely.
